data.description: Step into a modern comfort with this stunning home featuring a sleek black garage door, a stylish smoked glass front door, a beautiful and upgraded light fixtures that illuminate every corner. Enjoy the open-concept living area flooded with natural light, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, a beautiful and wide farm sink, a stainless steel gas oven range, a dishwasher, a microwave, and a spacious pantry.  Can’t miss the fully fenced and landscaped with sprinklers, this home is a true oasis. Not to mention, it sits on a corner lot!  Don't miss out, set up a showing with your favorite realtor today!   The Realtor has an ownership interest in the property.
